# SheShine — Cursor AI Rules
# Shopify Dawn Theme Development
# UK Women's Beauty & Personal Care Store

## 🎯 PROJECT OVERVIEW
You are building a professional, conversion-optimised Shopify storefront for **SheShine** — a UK-based women's beauty and personal care brand. The base theme is **Shopify Dawn**. Every file you create or edit must follow the rules below exactly.

---

## 🎨 BRAND IDENTITY — NEVER DEVIATE

### Logo Colors (Extracted from actual logo)
- "She" text color: `#CC92C5` (Light Mauve)
- "shine" text color: `#674170` (Deep Plum)
- Mid blend: `#AC7EA9`

### Full Brand Palette
```
--color-primary:       #674170;   /* Deep Plum — main CTA, headings */
--color-primary-dark:  #4a2e52;   /* Hover states */
--color-secondary:     #AC7EA9;   /* Mid Mauve — accents, borders */
--color-accent:        #CC92C5;   /* Light Mauve — badges, highlights */
--color-soft:          #EDD9EB;   /* Very light lilac — section backgrounds */
--color-bg:            #fdf7f5;   /* Off-white — page background */
--color-white:         #ffffff;
--color-text:          #1a1a1a;   /* Body text */
--color-text-muted:    #6b6b6b;   /* Subtext */
--color-border:        #e8d5e6;   /* Soft purple-toned border */
```

### Typography
```
Headings: "Cormorant Garamond", serif  — weights: 400, 600, 700
Body:     "Montserrat", sans-serif     — weights: 400, 500, 600
```
- Import via Google Fonts in `layout/theme.liquid`
- NEVER use system fonts, Inter, Roboto, or Arial

### Button Style
- Border-radius: `999px` (fully rounded pill shape)
- Primary: `background: #674170`, `color: #ffffff`
- Secondary: `background: transparent`, `border: 2px solid #674170`, `color: #674170`
- Hover: scale(1.03) + slight shadow

### Text on Colored Backgrounds
- On `#CC92C5`, `#AC7EA9`, `#EDD9EB` backgrounds → use `#4a2e52` text (NEVER white)
- On `#674170` background → use `#ffffff` text
- On `#fdf7f5` background → use `#1a1a1a` text

