## 🏗️ SHOPIFY DAWN THEME RULES

### File Structure
```
assets/          → CSS, JS, images, fonts
config/          → settings_schema.json, settings_data.json
layout/          → theme.liquid (main wrapper)
sections/        → .liquid section files
snippets/        → reusable .liquid partials
templates/       → JSON page templates
locales/         → translation files
```

### Every Section File MUST Have:
1. A complete `{% schema %}` block at the bottom with:
   - `"name"` — human-readable section name
   - `"settings"` array — all editable options (colors, text, images, toggles)
   - `"presets"` — so it appears in Shopify Theme Customiser "Add Section"
   - `"max_blocks"` if using blocks
2. Shopify Customiser-editable options for ALL content (text, colors, images, toggle show/hide)
3. Responsive design: mobile-first CSS

### Liquid Best Practices
- Use `{{ section.settings.SETTING_NAME }}` for all editable content
- Images: always use `| image_url: width: 800` filter + `loading="lazy"`
- Colors: use `{{ section.settings.bg_color }}` so merchant can edit in Customiser
- NEVER hardcode text strings — always make them schema settings
- Use `{% liquid %}` tag for multi-line logic
- Prefix all section CSS classes with `sheshine-` to avoid Dawn conflicts

### CSS Rules
- Link `sheshine-global.css` in every section via `{{ 'sheshine-global.css' | asset_url | stylesheet_tag }}`
- Use CSS custom properties (variables) for all colors — never hardcode hex values inline
- Mobile breakpoint: `max-width: 768px`
- Tablet breakpoint: `max-width: 1024px`

---

## ✨ ANIMATIONS — ALWAYS INCLUDE

### Scroll Reveal (IntersectionObserver — NOT scroll event listener)
```javascript
const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
  entries.forEach((entry, i) => {
    if (entry.isIntersecting) {
      setTimeout(() => entry.target.classList.add('is-visible'), i * 80);
    }
  });
}, { threshold: 0.1 });
document.querySelectorAll('.reveal').forEach(el => observer.observe(el));
```

### CSS Animation Classes (in sheshine-global.css)
```css
.reveal {
  opacity: 0;
  transform: translateY(20px);
  transition: opacity 0.6s ease, transform 0.6s ease;
}
.reveal.is-visible {
  opacity: 1;
  transform: translateY(0);
}
@keyframes marquee {
  from { transform: translateX(0); }
  to   { transform: translateX(-50%); }
}
@keyframes float {
  0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0px); }
  50%       { transform: translateY(-12px); }
}
@keyframes shimmer {
  from { background-position: -200% 0; }
  to   { background-position:  200% 0; }
}
```

### Performance Rules
- All animations use ONLY `transform` and `opacity` (GPU composited — no layout thrash)
- No `top/left/width/height` animations
- IntersectionObserver always over scroll event listeners
- Vanilla JS only — NO jQuery, NO external animation libraries

---

## 📐 LAYOUT & DESIGN SYSTEM

### Section Spacing
- Desktop padding: `80px 0`
- Mobile padding: `48px 0`
- Container max-width: `1280px`, centred with `margin: 0 auto`
- Inner padding: `0 24px` (mobile), `0 48px` (tablet), `0 80px` (desktop)

### Product Cards
- Border-radius: `16px`
- White background with subtle shadow on hover
- Image ratio: always `aspect-ratio: 1/1` (square)
- "SAVE X%" badge: `#674170` pill, white text, top-left
- "NEW" badge: `#AC7EA9` pill, white text, top-left
- Add to Cart button: full width, rounded pill, `#674170`
- Hover: `transform: scale(1.02)`, shadow deepens — `transition: 0.3s ease`

### Grid System
- Product grids: 4 columns desktop / 2 columns mobile
- `gap: 24px` desktop, `gap: 16px` mobile
- Use CSS Grid: `grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(220px, 1fr))`

### Marquee Strips
- Duplicate content for seamless loop (2x content, animate -50%)
- Edge fade: `mask-image: linear-gradient(to right, transparent 0%, black 8%, black 92%, transparent 100%)`
- Always add `pause on hover`: `:hover .marquee-track { animation-play-state: paused; }`

